{"tid":2416867,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"酒吧業協會稱再有70間酒吧結業　累計210間已結業","createTime":"2021-02-21T11:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T13:53:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0bbab440fa533089d5b2ea3558163f531f4c4b6","tid":2416867,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576685-20210221.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576685-20210221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnUBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=dd3c6478\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576685-20210221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=161934c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576685-20210221.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港酒吧業協會統計發現，農曆新年期間再多70間酒吧結業，佔全港酒吧總數約5%。連同早前結業的酒吧，累計有210間酒吧結業，佔總數約15%。<br />\n<br />\n協會表示，酒吧業已出現第二輪結業潮，部分酒吧因出現資金問題而結業或被封舖。亦有老闆及基層員工因酒吧停業，難以養活家庭。<br />\n<br />\n協會副主席錢雋永形容酒吧業已處於萬丈深淵，希望政府盡快容許酒吧復業。如政府繼續要求酒吧停業，應提供每間酒吧最少50萬元，讓他們渡過難關。"},{"pid":"2e9cc2897a6be92dfae0da8fdf513a4ed57a39f3","tid":2416867,"uid":21962,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:50:21.000Z","msg":"開檔？<br />\n宣誓先啦<br />\n之後只可以賣青島茅台咪俾你開囉"},{"pid":"d8524315f57d7f0777eb1c3f69858bae5657e322","tid":2416867,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"呵呵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db90bf64e588e0dbc0917485d86cf562776dd88","tid":2416867,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"做生意包賺？"},{"pid":"7ff8ac2b5adee4735b19d02100d828f3103c0e2a","tid":2416867,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"轉行派米囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.